              Every Sunday I'm on radio...
          .medium-6.columns
            %p
              Join the tribe of <a href ="www.kickarts.org.nz">KickArts</a>, Auckland's comprehensive artshow, on air every Sunday on 104.6 FM - Auckland area only - or on the <a href="www.planetaudio.org.nz/kickarts">PlanetAudio</a> website.
