          .medium-6.columns
            %p
              Besides co-hosting I've coded and designed the <a href ="www.kickarts.org.nz">KickArts</a> webpage at with the help of my colleague Benji Dalton.
            %p
              Benji and I have co-founded <a href ="www.webkea.co.nz">WebKea</a>, where we can create a brilliant online presence for you personally or for your business.
